ze is crucial for an optimal kitesurfing experience</strong>.</p><h2>How it=
 works</h2><p>Our calculator takes into account essential factors such as y=
our weight, the wind speed, your experience level, and your preferred ridin=
g style to recommend the most suitable kite size for you.</p><ul role=3D"li=
